So, Emery, your skin graft
is looking great.

04:15.775 --> 04:18.488
It should only be a few more weeks,
and we'll have you in physical therapy.

04:18.519 --> 04:20.442
No. I have to be out of here
by this Saturday.

04:20.797 --> 04:21.771
Why, you got a ho...

04:21.873 --> 04:24.306
<i>Careful. He's a burn victim.
Don't say "Hot date".</i>

04:24.390 --> 04:25.495
Hot rendezvous?

04:25.777 --> 04:26.617
<i>Damn it!</i>

04:26.745 --> 04:28.523
No. It's my high school graduation.

04:29.040 --> 04:31.401
Look, all my friends are going
off to different colleges.

04:31.484 --> 04:33.399
This is the last time
that we'll be together.

04:33.822 --> 04:35.516
Please, just don't make me miss this.

04:35.816 --> 04:37.168
I'll see what I can do.

04:40.281 --> 04:42.172
Turk, don't forget to get your
shift covered tonight.

04:42.209 --> 04:44.125
It's the 6th year anniversary
of our first date.

04:44.912 --> 04:49.496
I hope the present you got me is a good one,
because the one I got you is slammin'!

04:49.556 --> 04:51.635
- I can't wait.
- Ok.

04:52.476 --> 04:54.795
So what's the big gift there, Gordon?

04:55.209 --> 04:57.306
- Who?
- Black guy from "Sesame Street".

04:57.678 --> 05:01.920
Oh, well. The past couple of months
I've secretly been taking classes,

05:01.949 --> 05:05.464
and listening to tapes, and I have
learned Spanish for my baby.

05:05.902 --> 05:07.324
That's fantastic.

05:07.325 --> 05:10.510
It only took you 6 years to learn
the language that your wife speaks.

05:10.677 --> 05:13.068
Hey!
I've been eavesdropping.

05:13.531 --> 05:16.294
I got Lady a real gift
for our 1-month anniversary.

05:16.679 --> 05:18.841
I cured her fear of the unknown.

05:19.509 --> 05:22.383
Women are like crows.
They like shiny things.

05:22.705 --> 05:26.562
Classy stuff they can wear in their ears,
around their necks, through their nipples.

05:26.929 --> 05:28.070
Crows have nipples?

05:28.792 --> 05:31.188
Don't listen to them C-bear,
it's an amazing gift.

05:31.590 --> 05:34.516
Plus, you know how everyone's rude
to those day laborers across the street?

05:34.636 --> 05:36.654
Now we can finally talk to them.

05:42.145 --> 05:45.703
- Do you have work?
- No we just wanted to say "hi".

05:46.015 --> 05:47.499
How are you guys doing?

05:50.112 --> 05:52.275
Congratulations, my brothers.

05:52.417 --> 05:58.768
You have treated us with basic human
compassion and will now be rewarded...

05:58.803 --> 06:05.730
with a trip to the magical paradise
known has Amigoville.

06:08.309 --> 06:10.809
Your magical paradise is a park?

06:10.829 --> 06:14.380
Our people loves the picnics.

06:14.847 --> 06:17.486
Turk, look at the size of this churro!

06:17.814 --> 06:21.461
And over there, there's
a lake filled entirely with guacamole.

06:22.180 --> 06:24.795
Would you like a massage
from one of those beautiful ladies?

06:26.161 --> 06:28.088
No I can't. I'm married.

06:28.252 --> 06:29.489
Not a problem.

06:30.973 --> 06:32.822
I'll take the front.

06:33.228 --> 06:34.930
I'll massage your back.

06:35.264 --> 06:37.236
What a beautiful babes!

06:38.080 --> 06:40.347
What do you think of this place?

06:40.643 --> 06:43.088
I'm sorry. I don't
speak the spanishita.

06:43.371 --> 06:44.946
Is that gonna be a problem?

06:50.513 --> 06:52.639
Do you guys have an idea when
the black guy is coming down,

06:52.645 --> 06:53.960
because he has the car keys.

06:56.119 --> 06:56.868
Idiot!

